        "## Insights & Recommendations\n",
        "\n",
        "1. **Holiday Spikes:** As clearly visible in the trend plot, the late November period (around Black Friday) accounts for the highest single-day revenue peaks, followed by mid-December. *Recommendation: Allocate the largest marketing and operational budgets to these two windows.*\n",
        "2. **Weekend Lift:** Revenue shows a consistent dip mid-week and rises towards the weekend. *Recommendation: Schedule promotional email campaigns for Thursday evenings to capture the weekend purchasing momentum.* "
